  "description": [
    "A h AFTERNOON AUGUST 4 1953 HORSELESS CARRIAGE North Ctrotlnas Horseless Carriage Club passed through Lillington Thursday afternoon en route from Laurinburg to Raleigh on their annual tour Not all the fun was reserved for the drivers majority dressed in clothes to match the age of their vehicles and accom panted by their families Several hundred spectators were an hand in Lillington for the review of 55 highly polished old model cars ranging from the 1908 Reo to many models of the twenties Com mcnted one spectator It was more fun than a circus Cars refueled at Central Gulf Station parked at the courthouse square where they were treated to ice water and cokes by the Lillington Cham ber of Commerce Town board members were on hand to greet visitors London Is Suffering From Nude Shortage LONDON P There is such a scarcity of nude women in Britain that producer Dick Hurran may take the question to Parlia ment Hurran is so distracted trying to find enough nudes to take part in a London production of the famed French Folies Fergere that he may seek a law forbidding the ex port of undraped British females The thing reached a crisis"
